{"id":242,"parent_id":238,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":242,"title":"James 4","subtitle":"","short_title":"James","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/4","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 4"],[".studySummary",["i","Wars are born of lusts—The friends of the world are the enemies of God—Sin is failure to walk in the light we have received."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/4.1","order":"03.22.004.25079"},["b","1"],"From whence",["i","come"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"wars"],"and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"fightings"],"among you?",["i","come they"],"not hence,",["i","even"],"of your",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_1c"},"lusts"],"that war in your members?"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/4.2","order":"03.22.004.25080"},["b","2"],"Ye lust, and have not: ye kill, and desire to have, and cannot obtain: ye fight and war, yet ye have not, because ye ask not."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/4.3","order":"03.22.004.25081"},["b","3"],"Ye",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"ask"],", and receive not, because ye",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"ask"],["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_3c"},"amiss"],", that ye may",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_3d"},"consume"],["i","it"],"upon your",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_3e"},"lusts"],"."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/4.4","order":"03.22.004.25082"},["b","4"],"Ye",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"adulterers"],"and adulteresses, know ye not that the friendship of the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"world"],"is",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_4c"},"enmity"],"with God? whosoever therefore will be a friend of the world is the",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_4d"},"enemy"],"of God."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/4.5","order":"03.22.004.25083"},["b","5"],"Do ye think that the scripture saith in vain, The spirit that dwelleth in us lusteth to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"envy"],"?"],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/4.6","order":"03.22.004.25084"},["b","6"],"But he giveth more",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"grace"],". Wherefore he saith, God resisteth the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"proud"],", but giveth grace unto the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_6c"},"humble"],"."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/4.7","order":"03.22.004.25085"},["b","7"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"Submit"],"yourselves therefore to God.",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"Resist"],"the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_7c"},"devil"],", and he will flee from you."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/4.8","order":"03.22.004.25086"},["b","8"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"Draw"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"nigh"],"to God, and he will draw nigh to you.",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_8c"},"Cleanse"],["i","your"],"hands,",["i","ye"],"sinners; and",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_8d"},"purify"],["i","your"],"hearts,",["i","ye"],"double minded."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/4.9","order":"03.22.004.25087"},["b","9"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"Be afflicted"],", and mourn, and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"weep"],": let your laughter be turned to",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_9c"},"mourning"],", and",["i","your"],"joy to heaviness."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/4.10","order":"03.22.004.25088"},["b","10"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"Humble"],"yourselves in the sight of the Lord, and he shall lift you up."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/4.11","order":"03.22.004.25089"},["b","11"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"Speak"],"not evil one of another, brethren. He that speaketh evil of",["i","his"],"brother, and judgeth his brother, speaketh evil of the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"law"],", and judgeth the law: but if thou judge the law, thou art not a doer of the law, but a judge."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/4.12","order":"03.22.004.25090"},["b","12"],"There is one lawgiver, who is able to save and to destroy: who art thou that",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"judgest"],"another?"],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/4.13","order":"03.22.004.25091"},["b","13"],"Go to now, ye that say, To day or to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"morrow"],"we will go into such a city, and continue there a year, and buy and sell, and get gain:"],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/4.14","order":"03.22.004.25092"},["b","14"],"Whereas ye know not what",["i","shall be"],"on the morrow. For what",["i","is"],"your life? It is even a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"vapour"],", that appeareth for a little time, and then vanisheth away."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/4.15","order":"03.22.004.25093"},["b","15"],"For that ye",["i","ought"],"to say, If the Lord will, we shall live, and do this, or that."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/4.16","order":"03.22.004.25094"},["b","16"],"But now ye rejoice in your",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"boastings"],": all such rejoicing is evil."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/4.17","order":"03.22.004.25095"},["b","17"],"Therefore to him that",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"knoweth"],"to do good, and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_17b"},"doeth"],["i","it"],"not, to him it is",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_17c"},"sin"],"."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/4.1a","order":"03.22.004.25096"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/war"},"TG War"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/4.1b","order":"03.22.004.25098"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/apostasy-of-the-early-christian-church"},"TG Apostasy of the Early Christian Church"],"."],["div",{"id":"1c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/4.1c","order":"03.22.004.25100"},["b","1c"],["span.small","GR"],"pleasures, gratifications, passions."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/4.3a","order":"03.22.004.25102"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/prayer"},"TG Prayer"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/4.3b","order":"03.22.004.25104"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/10.5.4-6"},"Hel. 10:5 (4–6)"],"."],["div",{"id":"3c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/4.3c","order":"03.22.004.25106"},["b","3c"],["span.small","GR"],"wickedly, wrongly.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/8.26.26-27"},"Rom. 8:26 (26–27)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/46.30.28-30"},"D&C 46:30 (28–30)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/88.65.64-65"},"88:65 (64–65)"],"."],["div",{"id":"3d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/4.3d","order":"03.22.004.25108"},["b","3d"],["span.small","GR"],"waste, expend.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/46.9"},"D&C 46:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"3e","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/4.3e","order":"03.22.004.25110"},["b","3e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/lust"},"TG Lust"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/4.4a","order":"03.22.004.25112"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/whore"},"TG Whore"],"."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/4.4b","order":"03.22.004.25114"},["b","4b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/world"},"TG World"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/worldliness"},"Worldliness"],"."],["div",{"id":"4c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/4.4c","order":"03.22.004.25116"},["b","4c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/opposition"},"TG Opposition"],"."],["div",{"id":"4d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/4.4d","order":"03.22.004.25118"},["b","4d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/enemies"},"TG Enemies"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/4.5a","order":"03.22.004.25120"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/envy"},"TG Envy"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/4.6a","order":"03.22.004.25122"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/grace"},"TG Grace"],"."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/4.6b","order":"03.22.004.25124"},["b","6b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/pride"},"TG Pride"],"."],["div",{"id":"6c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/4.6c","order":"03.22.004.25126"},["b","6c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/poor-in-spirit"},"TG Poor in Spirit"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/4.7a","order":"03.22.004.25128"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/reconciliation"},"TG Reconciliation"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/submissiveness"},"Submissiveness"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/4.7b","order":"03.22.004.25130"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/abstain"},"TG Abstain"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/self-mastery"},"Self-Mastery"],"."],["div",{"id":"7c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/4.7c","order":"03.22.004.25132"},["b","7c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/devil"},"TG Devil"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/4.8a","order":"03.22.004.25134"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-presence-of"},"TG God, Presence of"],"."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/4.8b","order":"03.22.004.25136"},["b","8b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/69.18"},"Ps. 69:18"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/88.63"},"D&C 88:63"],"."],["div",{"id":"8c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/4.8c","order":"03.22.004.25138"},["b","8c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/repent"},"TG Repent"],"."],["div",{"id":"8d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/4.8d","order":"03.22.004.25140"},["b","8d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/purification"},"TG Purification"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/purity"},"Purity"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/james/4.9a","order":"03.22.004.25142"},["b","9a"],["span.small","GR"],"Endure hardship, Suffer harassment."],["div",{"id":"9